node.text: @shirleyhumblekitchen You’ve a yummilicious week too, dear! 😍
Yums @shirleyhumblekitchen

Wishing everyone a Blessed new week ahead! ❤️💛❤️💛
Last night,I try to replicate my old mum’s hakka dish:-
#南乳扣肉 #南乳芋头扣肉
Braised taro/yam, pork bellies with fermented red bean curds.
We will use it to ‘kip’ our store-bought mantou or plan leaf buns for lunch later.

#braised #braisedporkbelly #redfermentedbeancurd #hakkacusine #redfermentedporkbelly#braisedporkbelly #yam#taro#homecooking#homecook#icook#food#singaporehomecook #sgcooking#circuitbreakersg #sgunited#stayhomestaysafe
